# SpriteRenderSystem

## Purpose
Engine render bridge for world-space sprites: sole adder of DrawSpriteInFrameEvent. Each frame it emits
one in-frame draw event per entity that has both a SpriteComponent and a resolved
WorldTransformComponent, building a sprite from the world matrix, the component's sub-texture rectangle
and texture id, and the world transform's render sort key. Sprites without a world transform yet are
skipped. Registered by the engine in Application::Init.

## Input Components
| Component | Access | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| SpriteComponent | read | Sub-texture rectangle + texture id |
| WorldTransformComponent | read | World matrix + render sort key |

## Output Components
| Component | Access | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| DrawSpriteInFrameEvent | add (inframe) | One per drawable sprite; consumed by Renderer2DSystem this frame |
